# API Configuration
# =================

# For local development (backend running on localhost)
# Uncomment this line when developing locally:
# REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1

# For production (Vercel deployment)
# Set this in your Vercel project's Environment Variables dashboard
# Example: https://your-backend.herokuapp.com/api/v1
# or if using Vercel for backend: https://your-backend.vercel.app/api/v1
REACT_APP_API_URL=

# Note: Leave blank to use relative URLs (/api/v1)
# This will work if your backend is proxied or on the same domain
